<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="K_5736" type="Brief"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Andrea Podestà an Alfred Escher, Genua, Sonntag, 08. Mai 1870</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>Digitale Briefedition Alfred Escher, Zürich: Alfred Escher-Stiftung.</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><msDesc><msIdentifier><institution>SBB Historic</institution><idno>VGB_GB_SBBGB01_006</idno></msIdentifier></msDesc><bibl type="printed"/></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><textClass><keywords scheme="http://briefedition.alfred-escher.ch/keywords"><term>Gotthardbahnprojekt</term><term>Öffentliche Beteiligungen (Infrastruktur)</term></keywords></textClass><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName key="Podestà Andrea" type="addressee">Andrea Podestà</persName><persName key="Escher (vom Glas) Alfred" type="sender">Alfred Escher</persName><placeName>Genua</placeName><date when="1870-05-08">08. Mai 1870</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><placeName>Zürich</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="previous" target="B6550"/><ref type="next" target="B5299"/><ref type="next-in-corresp" target="B5741"/><ref type="previous-in-corresp" target="B5037"/></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><front>
      <div type="annotation"><p rend="left" xml:id="K_5736_p1"><lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
        <hi rend="underline">riservatissima</hi>
      </p> </div>
      
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_5736_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>
          <hi rend="printed">CABINETTO DEL SINDACO</hi>
        </p>
      
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_5736_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>
          <placeName key="Genua (I)">Genova</placeName>
          <lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>
          <hi rend="underline">
            <date when="1870-05-08">8 Maggio 1870</date></hi>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_5736_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>
          <choice><abbr>Sig.</abbr><expan>Signore (Herr)</expan></choice> Escher
        <lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>Presidente del
        <lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>Comitato <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Gottardista</placeName> <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/><hi rend="underline"><placeName key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurigo</placeName></hi></p>
      </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5736_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>Mentre a moi parere le
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>cose di <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Gottardo</placeName> procedono innanzi
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>assai bene, i nemici di questo
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>valico fanno naturalmente
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>con crescente intensità sempre
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>i più grandi sforzi in contrario.
</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5736_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>Coll`ultimo mio telegramma
        
    <lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>io avvisava di ciò la <choice><abbr>S. V. Ill<add>ustrissi</add>ma</abbr><expan>Signoria Vostra Illustrissima (Euer Hochwohlgeboren)</expan></choice> </p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5736_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>Ora credo bene nell`interesse
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>dell`opera nostra di avvertire
        
     <lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>la <choice><abbr>S. V. Ill<add>ustrissi</add>ma</abbr><expan>Signoria Vostra Illustrissima (Euer Hochwohlgeboren)</expan></choice>, che il gruppo <placeName key="Mailand (I)">Mila<lb xml:id="p1-l20" break="no"/>nese</placeName>, composto in gran parte di
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>uomini d'affari e di costruttori,
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l22"/>è, sia per influenza materiale,

<lb xml:id="p1-l23"/>sia per influenza morale, un
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l24"/>utilissimo corporatore nostro in
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l25"/><placeName key="Italien (Königreich)">Italia</placeName>, che conviene averlo
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l26"/>consenziente ed interessato a
<lb xml:id="p1-l27"/>promuovere l'intrapresa del
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l28"/><placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Gottardo</placeName> –
</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5736_p8"><lb xml:id="p1-l29"/>Io avverto di ciò la <choice><abbr>S. V. Ill<add>ustrissi</add>ma</abbr><expan>Signoria Vostra Illustrissima (Euer Hochwohlgeboren)</expan></choice> <lb xml:id="p1-l30"/>come di cose avrai importante
        

<pb n="2"/><lb xml:id="p2-l1"/>per quelle disposizioni,
        
<lb xml:id="p2-l2"/>concerti ch'Ella anderà conve<lb xml:id="p2-l3" break="no"/>niente promuovere del di

        
	<lb xml:id="p2-l4"/>Lei Comitato.</p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5736_p9"><lb xml:id="p2-l5"/>E me le ripeto</p>
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_5736_p10"><lb xml:id="p2-l6"/>
Devotissimo</p>
      </div>
      <div type="signature">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_5736_p11"><lb xml:id="p2-l7"/>A Podestà
          <lb xml:id="p2-l8"/>Sindaco di <placeName key="Genua (I)">Genova</placeName> </p>
      </div>
    </back></text></TEI>